text:
「ひぁ、んぁ……ぁ、うぁッ……あ、アァ――――ッ！」
予想外の反応だ。 けれど、快楽という餌を前にお預けを知らない今の身体は、びくびくんと狂ったように跳ね続ける桂が与えてくる極上の悦を、もっともっと享受しようと、我欲のままに動き出す。 感じ入ってるのだろう最奥ばかりを、激しい動きで突き回した。
trans:
"Hyaa, ngh... ah, ahh... A-Aaah---!"
The reaction was completely unexpected. However, this body, which now knows no restraint when faced with the bait of pleasure, continues to convulse madly under Kei's exquisite touch. Driven purely by selfish desire, this body moves to indulge in more and more of the overwhelming bliss being given.  It relentlessly pounded into the deepest part, which seemed to be feeling it the most, with fierce intensity.
